Dr.Shilpa was very understanding and empathetic. She explained all the options available and let me choose the option  I am comfortable with rather than deciding for herself. 

The entire team is very particular  about hygiene which I have normally found missing at other dentists. 

Just carry a towel with you for wiping your own mouth / face during the process since they didn't provide anything when I visited. I had to used my own handkerchief.

I was also shown the x-ray on a screen and explained whyat the results of each option could be.

******** ** **** ******* ***** **** *****

The initial fears of a dental surgery dissapeared meeting Dr. Shilpa. She sets high hygenic standards and is meticulous in her work, all the while speaking to the patient and getting them to relax. She followed up regularly on Whatsapp after the treatment. I could also feel and see her attention to details and zeal to do a quality job. She ensured she checked the quality of her work with xrays after the implants and Xrays. I now feel confident to  come from Europe to get my dental work done in India much cheaper, but without compromising on the quality. I faced no troubles or discomfort after the surgery and could start eating normally next day onwards, though am still eating soft food as a precaution to allow the healing go well.
